This basic Weather Forecast App was created in under an hour to demonstrate that you do not need a dedicated mobile app to get your local forecast - the job can be done just as well using HTML5

As it was done quickly, the code is clearly rough around the edges (with no design layer)

adddomloadevent.js - (c)2006 Jesse Skinner/Dean Edwards/Matthias Miller/John Resig

For more info, see:
 * http://www.thefutureoftheweb.com/blog/adddomloadevent
 * http://dean.edwards.name/weblog/2006/06/again/
 * http://www.vivabit.com/bollocks/2006/06/21/a-dom-ready-extension-for-prototype
 * http://simon.incutio.com/archive/2004/05/26/addLoadEvent

